  <title>Occurrence and Diversity of Xanthomonas campestris pv. campestris in Vegetable Brassica Fields in Nepal</title>
  <URL>https://cn.bing.com/academic/profile?id=23c2130a769e3c8027724b06bfe2e2e3&amp;encoded=0&amp;v=paper_preview&amp;mkt=zh-cn</URL>
